ng at alcoa his tenure at alcoa led him to manage operations in the united states brazil and switzerland he started his career in alcoa in  as a construction superintendent at its alumar refinery in brazil gerdau ameristeel corporation he was the president of gerdau ameristeel corp from  thereafter as president and ceo from  united states steel corporation he joined united states steel in july  as executive vice president he became president and ceo in september  he serves on the board of directors of us steel and oversees the transformation of the company ensuring sustainable profitability throughout the business cycle industry positions held in steel industry he has held important positions – chairman director and executive committee member of steel manufacturers association presently he is the executive committee member and a director board member of word steel association the vice chairman of the american iron and steel institute aisi director board member of aisi and the chairman of the association’s policy and planning committee achievements he has won several awards for his contribution to industry – notable among them are  steel maker of the year by the association of iron and steel technology platts global metals awards ceo of the year  and award for steel excellence in  by american metal market outside industry his leadership roles have extended beyond the steel industry he is a member of the business council on competitiveness and the national petroleum council he is the director board member of allegheny conference on community development and a member of african american chamber of commerce of western pennsylvania’s presidential roundtable future vision with donald trump elected the president of the united states mario longhi said that us steel industry is hopeful of restoring  jobs lost during the earlier recessionary phase us steel is planning to accelerate its investments in view of the infrastructural growth expected during trump’s tenure it also will restore jobs longhi came to the helm of us steel when there was global overcapacity in steel us market was facing increasing competition from imports the oil crisis that reduced steel demand and several other issues longhi believes that innovation can help the steel industry survive the crisis through simulation of processes d printing latest technology such as embedded chips in metals that can send information wherever they are deployedwhether in ship automobiles or space crafts awards  platts global metals ceo of the year award contribute to successstorycom help our community grow with motivational stories articles  tips people born in novemberpeople born in  people from brazilfamous ceos famous in business learn from people who already made it start to success carlos ghosn story kazuo hirai success story dick costolo success story doug mcmillon success story vikram chandra success story yang yuanqing success story share this experts share their ideas success tips and secrets pin it share twitt share wats popular  most popular inspirational quotes from apj abdul kalam good thoughts for students famous motivational quotes from abdul kalam on students  most successful and inspiring differently abled people the dhoni story  only indian captain to win all icc trophies famous success quotes habits of unsuccessful people vs successful people flipkart story nike inc story journey of cristiano ronaldo to cr story popular next mario longhi filho  brecksville oh  intelius sign in we found mario longhi filho in brecksville oh mario longhi filho intelius found that mario longhi filho is a male between  and  years old from brecksville oh we have connected them to  addresses  phone and  relatives or associates get report now age mario longhi filho is in his s mario has lived in brecksville oh pittsburgh pa mario longhi filho zodiac signtaurus gendermale professional status chief executive officer and president at us steel corp get report now want to know more about mario get